Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.63,0:00:10.72,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.90,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.37,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.81,0:00:37.58,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Eye of the Midnight Sun \Narrived at the Witches' Forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:39.22,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,searching for a magic stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.59,0:00:42.35,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Wanting to take advantage of \Nthe chaos they were causing,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:45.02,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,the Diamond Kingdom came to steal \Nthe Queen of Witches' secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:47.02,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Million Lasers!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:51.90,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll just have to kill this chick first!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.90,0:00:54.40,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:01:00.58,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Your lessons got through to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:04.47,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Fanzell's former student Mars, who was \Nstill in the Diamond Kingdom's army,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.47,0:01:06.58,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,decided he would side with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:08.29,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you protecting us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:11.90,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,As Ladros said, we're traitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.90,0:01:14.17,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,And you lost your memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:17.64,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'm on your side, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.69,0:01:21.31,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Deflect it over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:23.47,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going on, but okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:33.03,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,By taking advantage of Asta's anti-magic, \Nthey successfully defeated Ladros.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.63,0:01:37.78,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But the moment they tried to finish off Fana\Nof the Eye of the Midnight Sun's Third Eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.78,0:01:39.95,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,who was weakened by Noelle's spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:41.95,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Fana!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.38,0:01:44.08,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,It's me! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:45.04,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you recognize me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:47.41,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,My student Fana?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.76,0:01:49.17,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Fana, who had lost her memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:52.00,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,fell into a deeper state of confusion \Nand tried to self-destruct, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.60,0:01:55.01,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Everything should just... disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:59.34,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and Mars risked their lives to stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:07.52,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go see the world together!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:11.65,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:15.11,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,It's a promise, Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:23.87,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Fana regained her memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:36.71,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1023,1)}Those Who Boost Each Other Up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:03:59.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:00.89,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:05.06,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't have done it without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.06,0:04:06.07,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.09,0:04:11.52,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,There is no reason for the weak \Nto stand on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:16.37,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I was born to break people like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.37,0:04:17.69,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,You're in my way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:18.98,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:23.49,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,The weak will perish,\N and only the strong will remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.21,0:04:29.87,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Someone as naïve as you \Ncannot win against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.80,0:04:33.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That was all your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:36.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you were able to \Nsave your childhood friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.31,0:04:40.18,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Is he your friend, Mars?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:45.38,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! So you made a friend \Nin the outside world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:47.39,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,No, I wouldn't say he's—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:52.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's totally my friend! \NWe did fight once, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:53.14,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.53,0:04:55.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:05:00.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you calmed down, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:02.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But what the heck happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:10.03,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid dummy! Why do you have to do \Nsuch drastic things every single time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:13.54,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Were you born just to try to kill yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:15.66,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You barely have any clothes on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:18.84,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,You're a magnificent student.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.84,0:05:21.05,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:23.09,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Master Fanzell!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:28.80,flashback,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Your powers exist to protect others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.17,0:05:31.18,flashback,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:32.21,flashback,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:40.15,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you're both alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:46.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So you barely remember anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:48.68,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:51.95,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,After the final training, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:56.42,flashback,Morris,0000,0000,0000,,I can hardly believe she's \Nstarted breathing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:06:02.21,flashback,Morris,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the power of the magic that bears \Nthe Phoenix's name? Or could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:04.29,flashback,Morris,0000,0000,0000,,How fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.29,0:06:06.92,flashback,Morris,0000,0000,0000,,We'll fit Fana with a mage stone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.17,0:06:11.46,flashback,Morris,0000,0000,0000,,What a disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:15.45,flashback,Morris,0000,0000,0000,,Not only did it fail to increase her \Nmagic, but she hardly has any left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:18.48,flashback,Morris,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that was the last dying ember of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:21.96,flashback,Morris,0000,0000,0000,,Get rid of her. She's of \Nno interest to me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:31.08,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,You poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.08,0:06:33.13,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,My old friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:36.12,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as it was long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:39.41,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Humans even hurt other humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:42.26,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish, I shall destroy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:46.51,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,But... I need your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:48.88,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,You will live on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:55.78,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any memories after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:59.00,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,It felt as though someone \Nelse entered my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:01.65,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Like I was being controlled...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.87,0:07:06.65,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,All I remember is that \Nperson's fierce hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:09.40,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What about the third eye \Nand pointy ears you had?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.26,0:07:13.41,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry. \NI don't know anything about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:15.11,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,You went through all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.11,0:07:17.06,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea, and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:20.74,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Mars, you don't need to \Nfeel bad about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:23.42,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, we got to meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:25.85,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I'll never let you go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:29.80,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Let's stay together forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:31.05,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:33.92,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,My, my! Aren't things heating up over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:38.43,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,He's stiffened up as hard as a \Nchunk of ore. How adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:42.40,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Childhood friends tragically torn \Napart and reunited by destiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:44.69,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That's really great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:47.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, he's bawling over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:49.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Finral?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:53.08,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm jealous and envious and bummed out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:55.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You don't have any childhood friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:58.44,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,No! I don't have any cute \Nchildhood friends like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:08:02.08,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Nope! Nope! Nope! Not one, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.05,0:08:02.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I have childhood friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:03.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of them, actually!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:08.41,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, I'm not jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.41,0:08:10.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd I just get slapped?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:12.84,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm royalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.23,0:08:18.35,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, why did the Eye of the \NMidnight Sun come to the Witches' Forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:27.90,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I still feel a strong desire in my head \Nto retrieve the magic stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:31.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Magic stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:34.83,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,So that means there's a \Nmagic stone in this forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:36.87,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry and go see the Queen of Witches!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:44.02,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,No, before that, we need to save Domina, \NMariella, and the wounded witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:51.63,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What is this ki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:55.63,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! His magical power should be gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:58.89,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:20.28,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that was some intense magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:25.82,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,It took forever to absorb it all. \NThanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:28.54,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I must admit, I thought I was going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:31.92,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Ladros... But your magic \Npower should've been depleted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.92,0:09:35.32,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I emitted it all, and then took it back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.32,0:09:39.76,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,You rely too much on your \Nmagic detection, Teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:44.50,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Really, though, why do all of you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:48.20,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,keep putting your own lives \Nin danger to protect others?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:51.11,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mars...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:54.15,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why I'm\N gonna end up killing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:04.34,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, some weirdo just showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:06.87,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't concern you,\Nso could you get lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:08.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's got lots to do with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.55,0:10:10.47,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He's my...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:11.88,main,asta,0000,0000,0000,,friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:21.60,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Why do all of you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:25.14,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,keep putting your own lives \Nin danger to protect others?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:28.19,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mars...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:31.19,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why I'm\N gonna end up killing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:41.41,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, some weirdo just showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:43.91,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't concern you,\Nso could you get lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:45.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's got lots to do with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:46.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He's my...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.13,0:10:48.37,main,asta,0000,0000,0000,,friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:50.33,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:53.24,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Mars!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:54.67,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I need to use a recovery spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:56.55,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I can't cast anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.06,0:11:00.93,italics,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to my body? Is my magic gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:06.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Just hang on! I'm gonna pound this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.49,0:11:10.30,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, wait a sec! You're that one guy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:13.52,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,The anti-magic knight or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:17.06,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I totally feel your pain, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.06,0:11:20.02,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I was born without a magic attribute myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.02,0:11:24.78,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Even when I was a kid, everybody made\N fun of me and called me bland.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:28.99,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,But hey, you're even more worthless than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.99,0:11:31.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say, you bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:32.80,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I kinda feel bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:34.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Give me some of your magic, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:37.61,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I would if I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:40.34,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:43.49,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Here. All yours if you can reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:49.43,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,What a great reaction! I think \Nwe'd make great partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:51.60,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna team up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:55.11,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,You can be my right-hand man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:58.65,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk to the Diamond Army for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:01.36,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Let's rise up through the \Nroyal army's ranks together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.73,0:12:05.49,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,We'll teach the guys who get all cocky \Njust because they've got talent a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:11.79,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding. I'm gonna make his \Nanti-magic powers all mine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.31,0:12:13.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.56,0:12:14.43,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:17.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the Wizard King\N of the Clover Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.81,0:12:22.67,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Wizard King? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:28.68,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I hate idiots! Million Lasers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.13,0:12:34.69,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about how you fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:38.43,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Without that spatial magic guy over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:41.44,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,you can't do a thing about \Nlong-distance spells, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:44.45,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,You make the perfect target!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:49.87,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,That ricochet trick won't work on me, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:51.97,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Recycle, recycle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:54.77,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you can win! Just give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:02.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:06.22,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You hurt my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:08.72,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And you won't get away with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:10.43,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.81,0:13:13.68,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:18.87,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,There are only two kinds of people\N in this world: the users and the used.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.87,0:13:23.31,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I won my way to the top by \Nusing the people around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.31,0:13:25.69,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna use Mars over there
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.69,0:13:29.95,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,and the girl next to him to \Nget myself even further ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:35.46,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll let the military use them \Nfor magic research until they die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:45.11,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? You're not \Nletting me get away with this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:49.14,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,You can be my stepping stone, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:53.54,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:56.52,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:09.74,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not good! My magic's draining away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:13.74,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I-It won't come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:16.55,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wait... You're kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.55,0:14:18.37,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,From this? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.68,0:14:21.37,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! Everything I've worked for...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.37,0:14:24.34,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! All I did was take my \Neyes off of him for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:26.73,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I'd made it to the rank of \Nthe Eight Shining Generals!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:27.88,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! Bad! Bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.90,0:14:32.25,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,No way! No way! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:38.60,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Did he really just throw this stupidly \Nheavy sword all the way up there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:41.50,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of decision was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.50,0:14:44.68,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell were you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.68,0:14:47.77,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! Shit! This is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:51.79,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me I'm gonna be \Ntaken out by a dumbass attack like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:55.24,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Stay back! Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:14:59.50,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't have made it this far on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.93,0:15:04.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,People taught me how to use \Nmy power and how to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:06.76,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We got through life or death \Nsituations together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:09.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We helped each other out \Nwhile improving how we fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:12.59,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I've been able \Nto react to the attacks
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:17.18,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,is because of something called "ki" \Nfrom back in my homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:18.43,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:20.84,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Where I come from, we've got this saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.84,0:15:24.19,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,"A warrior never goes back on his word."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.79,0:15:28.13,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You said you were going to \Nbecome the Wizard King, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:31.67,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Surpass your limits. Right here, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:34.37,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:37.53,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:42.92,flashback,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Sea Dragon's Cradle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.37,0:15:45.67,flashback,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:47.00,flashback,All,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.06,0:15:50.63,flashbackitalics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bet everything
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:52.55,flashbackitalics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,on this one attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:57.72,flashback,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a failure anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:16:02.04,flashback,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Sea Dragon's Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:06.05,flashback,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:08.48,flashback,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Let us help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:12.70,flashback,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:15.07,flashback,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,That attack of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:17.45,flashback,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,will end up being incredibly powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:18.45,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:28.55,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you kill anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.47,0:16:34.10,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Bull Thrust!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:40.10,flashback,All,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.49,0:16:42.25,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:44.93,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My special move was a complete success!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:48.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Friends are only meant to be used?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:52.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not my friends! My friends and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.23,0:16:55.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We boost each other up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:58.71,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.13,0:17:03.50,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop hurting people! Please spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:06.92,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Take out this sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:08.75,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get it out on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:12.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:13.43,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:17.39,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I know how strong you are,\Nso I'm not gonna get careless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:20.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,If I take it out and you attack me,\NI have no chance of winning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:23.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if I'd missed when I \Nthrew it at you, I would've lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:25.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an idiot, so I can't afford \Nto mess up to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:28.58,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,No, please... I-I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:30.92,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,If it doesn't come out, I'm gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:32.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's not enough to kill anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.81,0:17:34.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I missed your vital points on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.54,0:17:38.36,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! I thought I'd be able \Nto trick an idiot like him if I
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.36,0:17:40.34,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,tugged at his heartstrings, \Nbut he's not buying it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:41.73,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! Shit! Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:45.35,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,This twerp's been through \Nhis share of battles!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:49.59,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm gonna whack you \Nagain and knock you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.83,0:17:53.30,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:55.37,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,This is all of my remaining magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.37,0:17:58.30,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,If I attack him and he blocks it,\NI'm really finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:06.14,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to use reinforcement \Nmagic and force it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.76,0:18:10.02,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:13.40,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I've got enough left for two magic bullets...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.58,0:18:17.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:20.21,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,You're Fana, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.21,0:18:21.52,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Ladros!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:25.37,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how you got those powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.99,0:18:28.96,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,but use that huge magic of yours right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:32.59,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huge magic? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:34.92,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Quit playing dumb, and hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:35.97,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Do it or I'll kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.97,0:18:37.42,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:40.43,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Mars!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:43.93,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,The next shot will really kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:48.85,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.85,0:18:50.61,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,And there it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:52.41,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:55.32,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Time for the ultimate gamble!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:02.26,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,This magic's insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:06.20,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like my body's gonna burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:34.52,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,This is the greatest magic I've ever eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:38.61,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! This power \Nsurpasses the spirit's!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:41.45,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,It's not an amount a human can emit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.37,0:19:44.78,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Ladros, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:47.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:49.66,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Payback time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:54.79,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I tracked it with ki, but it was still \Nso fast that I couldn't dodge it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:02.47,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I've obtained the ultimate power!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:06.07,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,If I use this, the other Eight Shining \NGenerals don't stand a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:09.77,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Forget them! I can take \Nover the whole kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:10.81,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Woohoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:14.60,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I'll murder everyone who \Never looked down on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.92,0:20:19.19,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,But before that, I guess \NI'd better finish you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:23.00,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I won't get careless again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:26.49,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep hitting you with ranged \Nattacks that you can't block...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:30.37,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,until you're in pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:33.75,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.97,0:20:40.63,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,He's turned the tables.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:46.45,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Since he can use that sword, I thought \Nhe might be their descendant, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.17,0:20:51.41,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Show me who you really are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.89,0:21:01.25,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, how many more shots can \Nthat body you're so proud of take?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:02.32,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
