Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.69,0:22:53.27,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.93,0:22:57.93,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,How Does It Taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.95,0:22:57.22,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,How Does It Taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.41,0:23:10.57,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,This is the greatest magic I've ever eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:11.82,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:14.84,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that tastes very regal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.84,0:23:16.08,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,That's royalty for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:17.49,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.49,0:23:21.08,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes. Yours tastes a little mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.08,0:23:22.19,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.64,0:23:26.94,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,This tastes really nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.94,0:23:27.77,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Ladros!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.77,0:23:29.72,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,It tastes like pickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:33.78,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying that not only do I look \Nold, but my magic tastes old, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.78,0:23:35.75,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,You got it, Teach!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.75,0:23:36.93,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Tee-hee!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.49,0:23:42.08,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Queen of Witches, what did you do to Asta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.69,0:23:44.98,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta's grimoire is giving off an eerie light.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.98,0:23:48.69,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You almost look like... a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.69,0:23:51.65,main,vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 63: "It's Nothing."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.65,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 63\N\N{\fs18} It's Nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.65,0:23:53.82,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,A black meteor shoots across the sky.
